    Verse: 15
Tags:
  - Power
---
People want to demonstrate power, and that is a sickness even God cannot
cure. It is beyond curing, and they call it “spiritual ego.” When a man
becomes a little spiritual and people start loving him and respecting him,
giving him things, bowing to him, well, that’s where the problem starts.
